snippet.title: China attacking India: What are Modi's steps to prevent terror attack on India?

localized.description:
Terror Attack: China has began its cross border terrorism against India in Arunachal Pradesh . Prime Minister Narendra Modi is supposed to take steps in order to curb the terrorism.
